  "title": "Financial Statements - Lecture 5 - Statement of Comprehensive Income - IFRS",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 10530.0,
      "end_time": 11160.0,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 11160.0,
      "end_time": 12060.0,
      "text": "Else here."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12060.0,
      "end_time": 14190.0,
      "text": "And in this video, we&#39;ll be exploring the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14190.0,
      "end_time": 16700.0,
      "text": "of comprehensive income IFRS."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16700.0,
      "end_time": 19200.0,
      "text": "Remember in our last video, we covered the income statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19200.0,
      "end_time": 22050.0,
      "text": "which provides users with a measure of profitability."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22050.0,
      "end_time": 24630.0,
      "text": "The profit or loss at the bottom of the income statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24630.0,
      "end_time": 26760.0,
      "text": "is used as an opening number in the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26760.0,
      "end_time": 28560.0,
      "text": "of comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 28560.0,
      "end_time": 31800.0,
      "text": "This statement then adds or deducts more complex items,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31800.0,
      "end_time": 34440.0,
      "text": "which are, as yet, unrealized."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 34440.0,
      "end_time": 37080.0,
      "text": "This includes gains and losses from foreign currency"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 37080.0,
      "end_time": 39630.0,
      "text": "and adjustments to value of other assets and liabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39630.0,
      "end_time": 43080.0,
      "text": "at fair value, rather than historical cost, as well as"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43080.0,
      "end_time": 45960.0,
      "text": "other items, which are left for more advanced accounting"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 45960.0,
      "end_time": 46999.0,
      "text": "courses."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46999.0,
      "end_time": 48540.0,
      "text": "The statement of comprehensive income"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48540.0,
      "end_time": 51180.0,
      "text": "provides a broader definition of profit or loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51180.0,
      "end_time": 54630.0,
      "text": "one that includes both realized and unrealized amounts."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54630.0,
      "end_time": 56560.0,
      "text": "In order to understand unrealized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56560.0,
      "end_time": 59520.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll compare it to the concept of realized."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59520.0,
      "end_time": 61992.0,
      "text": "When you sell a service, the sale is in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61992.0,
      "end_time": 64200.0,
      "text": "Your company has provided the service to the customer"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64200.0,
      "end_time": 65069.0,
      "text": "already."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 65069.0,
      "end_time": 67440.0,
      "text": "Revenue from that sale would go on the income statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 67440.0,
      "end_time": 69010.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s realized."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 69010.0,
      "end_time": 71060.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 71060.0,
      "end_time": 73541.0,
      "text": "What if a company bought shares in another company?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 73541.0,
      "end_time": 75540.0,
      "text": "The value of the shares when they were purchased"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 75540.0,
      "end_time": 77437.0,
      "text": "was $950,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 77437.0,
      "end_time": 79770.0,
      "text": "And that would go on the statement of financial position"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 79770.0,
      "end_time": 82950.0,
      "text": "as an asset, because it has future economic benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 82950.0,
      "end_time": 84180.0,
      "text": "to the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 84180.0,
      "end_time": 86490.0,
      "text": "What if by the end of the year, those shares"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 86490.0,
      "end_time": 90180.0,
      "text": "had declined in value and were only worth $800,000?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 90180.0,
      "end_time": 92720.0,
      "text": "That would be a loss of $150,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 92720.0,
      "end_time": 97200.0,
      "text": "But because you still hold the shares, the loss is unrealized."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 97200.0,
      "end_time": 99780.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a paper loss, not a realized loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 99780.0,
      "end_time": 102240.0,
      "text": "because you have not sold the shares as yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 102240.0,
      "end_time": 104760.0,
      "text": "That unrealized loss, net of taxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 104760.0,
      "end_time": 106200.0,
      "text": "would be recorded on the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 106200.0,
      "end_time": 108540.0,
      "text": "of comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 108540.0,
      "end_time": 110640.0,
      "text": "Unrealized gains or losses are amounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 110640.0,
      "end_time": 113400.0,
      "text": "that have not been realized, because we still own or control"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 113400.0,
      "end_time": 116489.0,
      "text": "the item that has caused the gain or the loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 116489.0,
      "end_time": 118530.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s look at the structure of the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 118530.0,
      "end_time": 120090.0,
      "text": "of comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 120090.0,
      "end_time": 123150.0,
      "text": "Again, the statement starts with a heading, which must always"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 123150.0,
      "end_time": 124980.0,
      "text": "include the company name, the title"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 124980.0,
      "end_time": 127908.0,
      "text": "of the financial statement, and the time period covered."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 127908.0,
      "end_time": 129449.0,
      "text": "The statement of comprehensive income"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 129449.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132270.0,
      "text": "than lists the profit or loss, if the company&#39;s expenses"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 132270.0,
      "end_time": 134790.0,
      "text": "are greater than the revenues, from the income statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 134790.0,
      "end_time": 138960.0,
      "text": "first, followed by any other comprehensive income items."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 138960.0,
      "end_time": 141450.0,
      "text": "Here, I&#39;ve used the example of foreign currency"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 141450.0,
      "end_time": 143610.0,
      "text": "and fair-valuing investments."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 143610.0,
      "end_time": 145410.0,
      "text": "All the other comprehensive income items"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 145410.0,
      "end_time": 147600.0,
      "text": "must be listed net of tax."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 147600.0,
      "end_time": 150510.0,
      "text": "This means that any applicable tax amounts have already"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 150510.0,
      "end_time": 151740.0,
      "text": "been deducted."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151740.0,
      "end_time": 153920.0,
      "text": "Here, the other comprehensive income items"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 153920.0,
      "end_time": 156570.0,
      "text": "are an overall gain, but they could have just as easily"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 156570.0,
      "end_time": 158370.0,
      "text": "been an overall loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 158370.0,
      "end_time": 161370.0,
      "text": "These amounts, added or deducted from the beginning profit"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161370.0,
      "end_time": 165480.0,
      "text": "or loss amount, are equal to total comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 165480.0,
      "end_time": 168720.0,
      "text": "Again, remember that other comprehensive income amounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 168720.0,
      "end_time": 171840.0,
      "text": "are unrealized gains or losses."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 171840.0,
      "end_time": 174210.0,
      "text": "Pause the video to answer this check your understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 174210.0,
      "end_time": 175990.0,
      "text": "question."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 175990.0,
      "end_time": 179350.0,
      "text": "IFRS requires the statement of comprehensive income to be--"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184150.0,
      "end_time": 187570.0,
      "text": "the correct answer is C. A corporation may decide"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187570.0,
      "end_time": 191020.0,
      "text": "to combine comprehensive income and income in one statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 191020.0,
      "end_time": 195070.0,
      "text": "or have two separate statements, as I&#39;ve shown in this video."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 195070.0,
      "end_time": 196930.0,
      "text": "Why does IFRS require a statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 196930.0,
      "end_time": 198160.0,
      "text": "of comprehensive income?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 198160.0,
      "end_time": 201640.0,
      "text": "The developers of IFRS felt that unrealized gains and losses"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 201640.0,
      "end_time": 204520.0,
      "text": "of a corporation could have enormous impact on user"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 204520.0,
      "end_time": 205480.0,
      "text": "decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 205480.0,
      "end_time": 209620.0,
      "text": "And by ignoring these amounts, user confusion would result."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 209620.0,
      "end_time": 212050.0,
      "text": "By adding or deducting these unrealized amounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 212050.0,
      "end_time": 214630.0,
      "text": "from the more traditional definition of profit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 214630.0,
      "end_time": 217240.0,
      "text": "users would have a more comprehensive representation"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 217240.0,
      "end_time": 219190.0,
      "text": "of income, in order to make decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 219190.0,
      "end_time": 221600.0,
      "text": "about possible future outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 221600.0,
      "end_time": 224590.0,
      "text": "Remember that profit or loss from the income statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 224590.0,
      "end_time": 226270.0,
      "text": "is the opening balance in the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 226270.0,
      "end_time": 227722.0,
      "text": "of comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 227722.0,
      "end_time": 229180.0,
      "text": "The income statement is, therefore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 229180.0,
      "end_time": 231806.0,
      "text": "connected to the statement of comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 231806.0,
      "end_time": 233680.0,
      "text": "How is this statement of comprehensive income"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 233680.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "connected to the other financial statements?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239230.0,
      "text": "The amount or amounts of other comprehensive income"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 239230.0,
      "end_time": 241870.0,
      "text": "is used in the statement of changes in equity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 241870.0,
      "end_time": 245000.0,
      "text": "as part of the accumulated other comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 245000.0,
      "end_time": 247270.0,
      "text": "So again, the order of the statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 247270.0,
      "end_time": 249370.0,
      "text": "is the income statement first, the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249370.0,
      "end_time": 251800.0,
      "text": "of comprehensive income next, and then"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 251800.0,
      "end_time": 254680.0,
      "text": "the statement of changes in equity, which we&#39;ll be covering"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 254680.0,
      "end_time": 256920.0,
      "text": "in an upcoming video."
    }
  ]
}